summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the condemnation proceedings to acquire land and other property necessary for laying off, opening, widening and establishing of Southwest Roxbury Street under Ordinance 99805, King County Cause No. 743336; accepting the condemnation award for Parcel 21 in connection therewith; and making an appropriation from the Arterial City Street Fund for payment thereof and for additional interest on certain prior awards in said cause.
